This paper is about algorithm selection and performance prediction using machine learning, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of resources and parallelism, which relates to distributed systems (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper introduces a framework for categorizing ranking predictions, which could be relevant to computer engineering (cs.CE).
